    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271160</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_040_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おふたりは
私をかっこいいと
おっしゃいました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You both said I am "rad."</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271160</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_040_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも私は
あなた方の方が
うらやましいです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But, to be sincere, I would much rather
enjoy life the way you two do.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271228</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_040_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え？　オレらが？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? Like us?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271320</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_040_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あなた方は
何にだって
なれるんですから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You can be anything if
you put your mind to it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271424</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_040_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Suzu&gt;ちゃんは、
一族の頭領やってるのが
いやなの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Suzu&gt;, do you not like being
the chief of your village?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271608</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_040_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そ、そういうことでは
ありません。ただ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Th-That's not the case. However...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271608</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_040_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私にも他の可能性を
模索する機会があれば
どうだったのかと考えただけです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I do ponder about other possibilities.
How different my life would be
under different circumstances.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271688</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_040_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それがイヤってことじゃ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thinking about other possibilities isn't
always a bad thing, y'know...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_040_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271944</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_040_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いえ……でも
もう迷わないと
決めました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Indeed. However, I must not waver.
This is the path I chose to follow.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271944</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_040_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私は一族を率いなくては
ならないのですから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I must stay strong, as I am the only
one responsible for leading the ninja.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271944</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_040_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さぁ、先を急ぎましょう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>At any rate, let's move forward.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
